{"tid":1867182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係癌症病患 醫護罷工有冇諗過我地？","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T06:04:37.000Z","uid":153251,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67e7ba577a1ddd40747559efdd2f60825e3dde65","tid":1867182,"uid":153251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"我有淋巴癌，上星期入院去打化療之前因為武漢肺炎驚到訓唔著，大喊！<br />\n我唔想癌症未醫好又要怕中共肺炎。<br />\n估唔到醫護願意為咗我地行出黎罷工，我住院期間啲醫護真係好錫我，佢地根本唔捨得放低我地去罷工。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係點解佢地都要逼自己去罷工啊？因為佢哋保護緊我哋啊！<br />\n我想同佢地講，唔好咁自責，我地好多病人都好乖嫁，明白你係為咗香港人罷工。<br />\n見到佢地直播有醫護暈咗真係好心痛，我地唔要英雄，唔要犧牲，我地只要你哋平平安安，健健康康救更多既病人！<br />\n希望各位係呢段期間要保護好自己，唔好為醫護增加負擔，記住，市民先係第一道防線！！！<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以幫我推比罷工既醫護睇！多謝大家！"},{"pid":"2440c1e97fa81faceb94593fde725c720d82fd94","tid":1867182,"uid":285371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"開過個標題啦"},{"pid":"afeed5e5f404d2136e25561c9f1992a5efc8f013","tid":1867182,"uid":149266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fb6ea266729e54a9f8cf281c6c8698b12c01e2","tid":1867182,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e902923bea04b3981a119ca98f4c2ecbd5b558","tid":1867182,"uid":153722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"P牌仲要標題黨"},{"pid":"7b037c12645aba9f530d3022ac62212cbf32cdc1","tid":1867182,"uid":153251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afeed5e5f404d2136e25561c9f1992a5efc8f013","tid":1867182,"uid":149266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:31:10.000Z",